    "user_title": "Configure Zero-Trust Network Isolation for Claude Code",
    "value_statement": "Protect your AI coding environment from prompt injection attacks and data exfiltration. Configure trusted domain whitelists, proxy settings, and secure environment variable handling for safe development.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "Claude Code network security",
